          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1624354714314-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Tip: This is to warm your tortillas later – alternatively, add them to a plate and pop in the microwave for 1-2 min!</p><p>Wash the <strong>gem</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper </strong>and shred</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
