    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>pulled</strong> <strong>mushrooms</strong> to the pan with the <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> and cook for 2 min or until warmed through – these are your <strong>pulled hoisin mushrooms</strong></p>",
