    {
      "instruction": "<p>Assemble the wraps by dividing the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>spring onion strips</strong>, <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong> and <strong>pulled</strong> <strong>hoisin mushrooms</strong> between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
